posts.description:
"Life is a series of commas, not periods." --- Matthew McConaughey
________________________________________

Need support? It's here...❤️ Hoping to be inspired? Yes, every single day! Want more beauty, brains, bold spirits with super refined flair in your life? Got you covered 🙌🏼 Jonesin' to feel tickled from your toes to the top of your head and laugh so hard you'll cry? There's an app I know will do the trick! Instagram is so many things simultaneously and I've loved the moments shared here with you guys to the depth of my core!! Sometimes all it takes is seeing a genius post from one of you to turn my day around and I'm grateful, so grateful for that ☺️
________________________________________

My time on IG feels like it's run its course. Sean, the fur babes and I are looking forward to doing some refocusing. It's a good thing! I really wanted to let you know how much of your awesome shine I'll continue to carry with me. Having a chance to communicate with friends all over the world is such a cherished aspect I've loved being apart of here 🙏🏼 Thanks to each and every one of you! Your sparks have ignited so many of my days over the past few years ✨ Cheering loud for all of you... be well, stay stoked and inspired!! 😘💕📲💎🚀🎈🎠🍬☃💋👋🏼🐬🌺🍭🚨🌈🙊🎉🎬🙋🏻

"I know I’m not saving the world, but something in what I’ve learned how to do or the stories that I’ve tried to tell, they’re some sort of representation of how life is or how life could be. And that gives some sort of optimism. And an optimistic attitude is a successful attitude." --- Bill Murray
________________________________________
Thanks to @herhollowway for providing a new filler 📷 in my profile circle ⚪️👈🏼💜 You're the best Joc!!
Coolin' in the shadows... his fluffy sister, well she likes to run on ahead and give the joint a proper once over #🐕🌳

"You can spread jelly on the peanut butter but you can't spread peanut butter on the jelly." --- Dick Van Dyke

This yum is called the perfect peanut butter and jelly smoothie - and it is!! Recipe by @godairyfree 💜

"Happiness. It was the place where passion, with all its dazzle and drumbeat, met something softer: homecoming and safety and pure sunbeam comfort. It was all those things, intertwined with the heat and the thrill, and it was as bright within her as a swallowed star." --- Laini Taylor

Till the night closes in 🎤🌊💛 ________________________________________
Sweet slumbers and lovely lullabies everyone!
Found a little lichen colony. Reminds me of peeling paint... or flourishing florets 🌼
The kind of gem discoveries that make you wish they'd open up in your own neighborhood?! @nourishvictoria is one of those! 😋✊🏼💚

Honorable mentions to the wind ⛴🌬💨🙈 Channeling Cousin Itt and needing umpteen energy beverages💥☕️ Took a ferry ride to Victoria for a wedding in an apple orchard today... have a super Saturday you guys!! #imonaboat
